        "title": "Identity",
        "text": "$$\\tan(x)=\\frac{\\sin(x)}{\\cos(x)}, \\$$ $$\\cot(x)=\\frac{\\cos(x)}{\\sin(x)}, \\$$ $$\\csc(x)=\\frac{1}{\\sin(x)}$$",
